%% Diagram: VReplication-driven resharding workflow
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Op as Operator
    participant Topo as Topology
    participant VG as VTGate
    participant Src as Source shard
    participant Tgt as Target shards

    Op->>Topo: Reshard.Init (new ranges)
    Topo->>Tgt: Provision MySQL + VTTablet
    Note over Src,Tgt: 1 — Bulk copy + stream
    Tgt->>Src: VStream subscribe (binlog)
    Src-->>Tgt: Snapshot + tail events
    Note over Tgt: 2 — Catchup, lag → 0
    Op->>Tgt: 3 — VDiff verify
    Tgt-->>Op: Diff report (empty)
    Note over VG,Tgt: 4 — SwitchTraffic
    Op->>VG: SwitchTraffic (primary)
    VG->>Src: Stop writes, record GTID
    Note over Tgt: Catch up to GTID (≤ 30 s)
    Note over VG: Buffer queries (sub-sec)
    VG->>Topo: Atomic topology update
    VG-->>Tgt: Resume writes on targets
    Op->>Src: 5 — Drop source artifacts
